From eb407759b3e41b84549f64059fe4dc36c0054a09 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Felicitas Pojtinger <felicitas@pojtinger.com>
Date: Tue, 07 Jul 2026 23:39:14 -0700
Subject: [PATCH] feat: Add ad-hoc modal when selecting an element in the portfolio, generate image URLs at generation time

Signed-off-by: Felicitas Pojtinger <felicitas@pojtinger.com>
---
